    Description: Judgement
    Hexagram: "3 - \u4DC2 - Chun"
    Page: 27
  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
---
The incessant bickering and contests between chief and jealous kinsmen; the
weak central power; the divided jurisdictions; the obstinacy with which a
man of high birth insists on the proper punctilio to be reciprocated between
himself and his Chief -- all these are tokens of a free society in the rough.
